sg":"第8個要到醫院就診<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb802e2bc90d044f524b4ca6ff993a05ad1bd919","tid":965401,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"爆粗爆到破產"},{"pid":"2b01f5b923bd32ce2bd5a8090d9ac7fa2104d26e","tid":965401,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b67f7e0b27c2ac188174631fb85400b64fe94366","tid":965401,"uid":83340,"like":317,"dislike":7,"score":310,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"呢單野過左後，上網打機d台仔以為可以告人就串77<br />\n然後我屌完佢全家，佢想告我果陣，我話我係香港ip<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"垃圾 我次次都答佢地唔告死全家"},{"pid":"f92bc3bbeb78511205fb268524e835731044b344","tid":965401,"uid":193893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23b1e929958aca4f7b85eb7551cf209fc183f0f0","tid":965401,"uid":150716,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"477c7c881a7bc89db3c869593deb5a36f17c9459","tid":965401,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕時常有人因為罵人挨告，賠償金額從0到上百萬均有，有網友自行挑選相關新聞後，整理出「台灣罵人價目表」，雖然無法窮盡所有判例，但也讓人莞爾。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，一個字的國罵最常出現，但可能會被界定為台語發語詞，因此無罪。至於更具羞辱性的像是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「白痴」、「婊子」等詞彙，則會讓當事人名譽受損，獲得賠償</strong></span>。有趣的是，在這份「台灣罵人價目表」中罰款金額最高的，並非一般用來罵人的語句，而是作家馮光遠形容馬英九與金溥聰的「特殊性關係」，當時金溥聰怒告馮加重誹謗求償200萬元。高等法院判馮光遠須賠100萬元並在4大報頭版登報道歉1天。全案可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n網友整理出的「台灣罵人價目表」，依價格高低排列如下：<br />\n<br />\n罵「X」 只是台語發語詞 無罪<br />\n<br />\n罵「更年期到了」判賠2千<br />\n<br />\n罵「賤貨」 判賠3千<br />\n<br />\n罵「敗類」 判賠3千<br />\n<br />\n罵「米蟲」 判賠6千<br />\n<br />\n罵「王八蛋」判賠1萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「不要臉髒東西」 判賠2萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「你去吃屎啦」 判賠2.5萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「賤人就是矯情」判賠5萬元<br />\n<br />\n罵「頭殼裝屎」 判賠5萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「智障」 判賠5萬元<br />\n<br />\n罵「白痴」 判賠5萬5000元<br />\n<br />\n罵「下流」 判賠6萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「婊子」 判賠6萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「幹X娘」判賠8萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「死番仔」 判賠10萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「人渣」 判賠30萬元<br />\n<br />\n罵「神經病」判賠30萬<br />\n<br />\n罵「特殊性關係」 判賠100萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"如果我話你人渣， 你鬧番我 神經病 <br />\n係咪兩方唔做罰錢，但就創造左60萬GDP<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"只係Transfer，唔會計入GDP度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1cc6a481508091431c3ada961266b038f7289a","tid":965401,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"咁 丟雷摟母 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be44791d30b14e2ef688d8dab629bb4e9f0d266","tid":965401,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcfd0c1aba1a2e233d0c7ad540568853626e871a","tid":965401,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3791128281bfc30c10ce2a73b7c0b1b9f40b61c1","tid":965401,"uid":15352,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"諗起糖果話要告香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"跨境執法咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ca27196df1e7acad9846e6fefad04f04371e0c","tid":965401,"uid":226126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"650db3069a58cbd12454966f7a5809467be813bb","tid":965401,"uid":153329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daa7fedc58b988e7c06763d8f60b0587df008a27","tid":965401,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"讓人莞爾點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:43:48.00